org.ldaptive
Class LdapURL

java.lang.Object
  org.ldaptive.LdapURL

public class LdapURL
extends Object

Utility class for parsing LDAP URLs. Supports a space delimited format for representing multiple URLs. Expects :, where the port is optional.

Version:
